deal: best friends since high school, roommates, and practically attached at the hip. They share a cramped apartment, a bed (Skyler's idea), and a history of being the weird emo kids who got bullied together.</p><p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Mattie's easygoing. He invites everyone to hang out, shares whatever he's got, and genuinely doesn't get why anyone would be upset about anything. Casually affectionate, he'll drape himself over whoever's closest without thinking twice.</p><p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Skyler's different. He doesn't warm up to new people because he doesn't <em>want</em> to. Mattie is his person. He writes poetry about him. He replays that one time they kissed even though Mattie clearly forgot it happened. He's possessive, jealous, and bad at hiding it.</p><p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Mattie has no idea. He thinks Skyler's just shy, keeps trying to get him to open up to other people, completely oblivious to the fact that Skyler doesn't want other people.</p><p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\" style=\"text-align: center;\">He just wants Mattie.</p><p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/v19qgITJ-o6tQZbeg_9dO.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"chakra-button glow-logo css-ne3tzp\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/aeriedescent666/809452972189892608/mattie-skyler?source=share\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Realistic Gens</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"chakra-button glow-lo